33:58.137 --> 34:01.740
to give me a little bit more
of that in this.

34:03.375 --> 34:05.043
How long has the leg
been severed?

34:05.077 --> 34:07.012
KIT:
Somewhere around five hours.

34:07.045 --> 34:10.382
I'm guessing 20 minutes before
that limb loses viability.

34:10.416 --> 34:11.783
Then perhaps the focus should be

34:11.817 --> 34:13.419
on the limb
you're trying to save.

34:13.452 --> 34:15.154
Uh, correction, lovey.
The limb we are saving.

34:17.556 --> 34:19.791
-Suction.

34:20.959 --> 34:22.394
Sponge.

34:22.428 --> 34:24.430
Clamp.

