34:41.847 --> 34:44.483
New problem.

34:44.516 --> 34:46.885
He's bradying down.

34:46.918 --> 34:49.588
Get the ultrasound.

34:52.991 --> 34:56.128
Tamponade compressed his heart.

34:56.162 --> 34:58.164
The mediastinal bleed
must have opened up.

