39:50.456 --> 39:52.791
Hi.

39:52.824 --> 39:54.693
Hi. Um...

39:54.726 --> 39:58.129
Oh, it's-it's okay, sweetie.
It's okay.

39:58.163 --> 40:00.599
Daddy loves you, honey.

40:02.901 --> 40:05.904
Nice assist in the ER today,
Pravesh.

40:05.937 --> 40:07.439
Thanks, Dr. Austin.

40:07.473 --> 40:09.107
