in the OR...

40:09.140 --> 40:11.777
Shh. I know what I did well.

40:11.810 --> 40:14.079
Isn't this the loveliest part
of the job?

40:14.112 --> 40:15.647
What part are we talking about?

40:15.681 --> 40:17.215
The part that makes you want

40:17.248 --> 40:19.317
to pick up the phone
and call your own kids.

40:19.350 --> 40:22.187
American Bobtail and a Maine
Coon are the only kids I got.

40:24.155 --> 40:26.157
Wait. You have human kids?

40:26.191 --> 40:28.293
Two, from my first marriage.

40:28.326 --> 40:29.928
All grown now.

40:29.961 --> 40:32.130
And one of my kids has a kid.

40:32.163 --> 40:34.432
Good night, chaps.

40:37.035 --> 40:39.237
Her kid has a kid.

40:39.270 --> 40:41.439
She's a grandmother.

40:46.778 --> 40:48.680
You know, I...

40:51.950 --> 40:54.085
You know, I was thinking

40:54.119 --> 40:56.588
that this indelible session

40:56.622 --> 40:58.289
would be...

40:58.323 --> 41:00.659
One time. No strings.

41:03.028 --> 41:05.631
I now find myself reconsidering.

41:05.664 --> 41:09.535
-Me too.
-Hmm.

41:09.568 --> 41:11.336
I got to say,
my new assistant was right

41:11.369 --> 41:13.038
